 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/soldier18.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1749740\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1749740\"><span></span><p>A symbol that means a lot to many people....</p><p><span></span> YouTube/Marvel</p></figcaption></figure></li></ul></div><p><em>Listing image by <a href=\"https://www.marvel.com/\">YouTube/Marvel</a></em></p></div></div>","author":"Jennifer Ouellette","siteTitle":"Ars Technica","siteHash":"5b0ddf6e8923e49262a7894cfd77962733e43fbcc565a103b48373820b310636","entryHash":"1ac36cba89fcd4cb4c8aad8240289a7b63ffef24aaecff790ea4acfd35f1a043","category":"Tech"}